        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-10-17 13:08:36.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nFurther, here I see eclipselink being used, while in PIPEngineGetHistory.java I saw using hibernate, 2 competing JPA persistence implementations.   Probably not a good thing to use both implementations instead of sticking to one, may be that's giving you sideeffects.",
